{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"288384a42e","title":"反对党团员与积极分子的右派言论 （二）","origin":"《右派言论集》（河南医学院马列主义教研室编印，1958年4月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"658693c43f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"288384a42e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00d8e3d85b","name":"河南医学院"},{"id":"14094b12bc","name":"李国础"},{"id":"38babc55a5","name":"郭木轩"},{"id":"48b21ac680","name":"张蕴鑫"},{"id":"4a75983131","name":"张乃仪"},{"id":"53348bcf7d","name":"马伊"},{"id":"781b62c6c6","name":"黄钦昌"},{"id":"b8fa54c605","name":"刘延忠"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d451174ba2","type":"title","text":"反对党团员与积极分子的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"ef4e563912","type":"authors","text":"河南医学院马伊张蕴鑫李国础张乃仪黄钦昌郭木轩刘延忠","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"890a6d3498","type":"paragraph","text":"积极分子是一贯欺上压下，是“帮凶”“党棍”“小人”。(马伊，教务科干事)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"003b821cb1","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反积极分子是“黑邦”、“打手”奸险狡滑的东西。(张蕴鑫，24期学生)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"bb7feed8c7","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反中的左派先生们，你们无情打击，残酷斗争好人，你们给多少人带上罪名使他们名誉丧尽，惨伤心灵，你们污辱了多少青年，使他们吐血成肺病，你们破坏了党的政策，你们做了张廷辅的帮凶，你们有良心吗？你们认识了侵犯人权的罪行吗？(李国础)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"ce7f7e7a33","type":"paragraph","text":"积极分子是“狗腿”“爪牙”“帮凶”，是被法西斯麻醉了的打手，我要跟你们白刀子进去，红刀子出来。(张乃仪，医22期学生)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"0ffbef31b2","type":"paragraph","text":"每经过一次运动，就出现一批贵族，有些人是靠旧职员的血和肉作为自己起家的资本。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"098d00c61a","type":"paragraph","text":"党与群众之间有墙，这墙是假积极分子造成的。(黄钦昌，25期学生)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"1ce0f06f74","type":"paragraph","text":"“本三”年级(24期)是“哈巴狗”，光听领导的话，叫往哪里就往哪里跑。(郭木轩，25期学生)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"},{"id":"734f9c877c","type":"paragraph","text":"“本三”是“护校派”“打手班”。(刘延忠，24期学生)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e"}],"page":{"id":"0157dee432","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"288384a42e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}